data.description: 524 Ryan Dr, a stunning two-story home in Richmond, KY's Magnolia Point neighborhood, built by Payne Homes in 2019 on a .329-acre lot with a tranquil creek backdrop. The kitchen features upgraded cabinets and high-end stainless steel appliances. New carpet and hardwood flooring throughout add a touch of luxury.Spacious rooms provide versatility, and the basement includes a kitchenette and ample living space. The fifth bedroom, currently an office, can easily become a cozy bedroom. The sixth bedroom in the basement serves as a versatile bonus room.Magnolia Point offers a charming community vibe and convenient access to amenities, shopping, dining, and recreation. This exceptional home blends elegance, functionality, and potential. Schedule a private tour today.
